Boys' state qualifying cross country results Boys' state qualifying cross country results Prep Sports , Photos Iowa City West's Patrick Karanja run in a Class 4A high school state qualifying meet at the Seminole Valley Cross Country Course in Cedar Rapids on Thursday, Oct. 22, 2015. Karanja finished 4th with a time of 15:59.47. (Adam Wesley/The Gazette) Most Popular October 22, 2015 | 11:08 pm 
Results from state qualifying meets involving area teams, held in all classes Thursday. 
The top three teams and top 15 individuals at each site advance to the state meet in Fort Dodge next Saturday.
